high_descs: Turn left and cross the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Look down to face the apple in the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into slices.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple in the sink.
TUrn around to face the center table.
Place the apple piece in the pot on the center table.
Pick up the pot on the center table.
Turn around to face the sink.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a piece of apple in a pot plus move them to the sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in the middle of the sink.
With the knife in hand move over to the left side of the sink.
Slice the apple that is on the left side of the sink.
Place the knife on the edge of the sink on top of the spoon.
Pick up a slice of the apple that is in the sink.
With the apple in your hand turn around to the island counter directly behind you.
Place the apple slice into the round pot that is to the right of the knife on the counter.
Pick up the round pot with the apple slice in it that is on the counter.
With the round pot in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the round pot with the apple in it to the left of the tea pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Slice apple, put in pot and put in sink.

high_descs: move left to the sink
pick up the knife from the sink
head to the apple on the sink
slice the apple in the sink
drop the knife by the sink
pick up a slice of the apple
turn around to the table
drop the apple in the pot on the table
pick up the pot on the table
turn around and head to the sink
drop the pot in the sink
anns.task_desc: drop a pot with a  slice of apple in it in the sink
